# remove outlines
outliers <- function(x) {
  
  Q1 <- quantile(x, probs=.25)
  Q3 <- quantile(x, probs=.75)
  iqr = Q3-Q1
  
  upper_limit = Q3 + (iqr*1.5)
  lower_limit = Q1 - (iqr*1.5)
  
  x > upper_limit | x < lower_limit
}

remove_outliers <- function(new_df, cols = names(new_df)) {
  for (col in cols) {
    new_df <- new_df[!outliers(new_df[[col]]),]
  }
  new_df
}
